    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a pool ball and smash your enemies into the pockets or launch them straight off the table in this chaotic <strong>physics-based party brawler</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/042e4b25ef131a26cd2c74afe339fd4d.poster.avif?t=1771863114\" width=1170 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/042e4b25ef131a26cd2c74afe339fd4d.webm?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/042e4b25ef131a26cd2c74afe339fd4d.mp4?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Send your enemies flying in over 15 different modes!</strong> <br>From team-based brawlers and free-for-all modes to parkour challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/8eb57baadd6ccc4a39fcba75e4f92af3.poster.avif?t=1771863114\" width=1170 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/8eb57baadd6ccc4a39fcba75e4f92af3.webm?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/8eb57baadd6ccc4a39fcba75e4f92af3.mp4?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle your friends online, locally, or both at the same time!</strong><br>Jump into <strong>local multiplayer, online matches or mix local </strong>and online with up to 4 local players!   <br>Play with up to<strong> 8 players </strong>in chaotic<strong> public lobbies </strong>or in <strong>private lobbies, for you and your friends</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/11d7133a7345f10d3a5feac567804419.poster.avif?t=1771863114\" width=1170 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/11d7133a7345f10d3a5feac567804419.webm?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/11d7133a7345f10d3a5feac567804419.mp4?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock and choose from up to 50 different skins</strong>!<br>Choose the ball YOU really want to be, nobody can stop you! Be the ball you are meant to be!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/1ef651ed61f6e63b1a77647f677deae3.poster.avif?t=1771863114\" width=1170 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/1ef651ed61f6e63b1a77647f677deae3.webm?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043690/extras/1ef651ed61f6e63b1a77647f677deae3.mp4?t=1771863114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlist</strong> <strong>Billgard</strong> now ! &lt;3</p>",
